@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_muapwb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.49) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.11)) * v1)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.59)
    v2 = ((v0 * v1) + (wp.exp(v2 + 0.85) * v1))
    tmp = (v1 * (tmp + wp.exp(v2 + 0.23)))
    v2 = ((v1 * tmp) + v1)
    v1 = 0.10
    data[tid] = v0
